name: Amante De Las Alturas
description:
“Amante De Las Alturas” is a trap song that I recorded in early 2021 and it wasn't until now that I felt it was the best time to launch alongside the blockchain. This song is about one gurl that I met a few years ago and the good time that we have together. 

Artist- Sad Blu 
Producer- Miky, Sad Blu
